<h1 id="toc0"><span><span style="color: black"><em>Containment Breach The Musical</em></span></span></h1>
<hr />
<p><span style="font-size:80%;">From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.</span></p>
<p><em>This article is about the stage musical. For the book series, see <span style="color: #0645ad">Containment Breach</span>. For the film series, see <span style="color: #0645ad">Containment Breach (film series)</span>. For other uses, see <span style="color: #0645ad">Containment Breach (disambiguation)</span>.</em></p>
<div style="float:right; margin:0 2em 1em 2em; width:300px; padding:5px; border-style: solid; border-width:1px; border-color:#A0A0A0; background-color:#F0F0F0;">
<div style="text-align: center;">
<p><span style="font-size:120%;"><em><strong>Containment Breach</strong></em></span><br />
<span style="font-size:90%;"><em><strong>The Musical</strong></em></span></p>
<img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/containment-breach-the-musical/CBPlaybill.png" alt="CBPlaybill.png" class="image" />
<p>Broadway <span style="color: #0645ad">Playbill</span> cover</p>
